These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, ice-hockey, water-polo, volleyball
4 different games are played: whist, domino, canasta, poker
1. the person playing whist is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person playing domino is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing poker is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Sport   | water-polo | tennis  | ice-hockey   | volleyball    |
| Game     | whist     | canasta    | poker    | domino      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dannemann, havana, aristoff
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, zombie, romance, mystery
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the havana-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
7. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the aristoff-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Cigar   | havana     | tiparillo | aristoff  | dannemann |
| Movie-Genre     | mystery        | romance  | zombie    | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, dog, pony, rabbit
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, azalea, begonia, daffodil
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the person who growsdaffodil is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the rabbit##2
2. the person who growsazalea is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the pony##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsbegonia is between the owner of the dog and the person who growsdaisy##2
7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | fish | dog   | rabbit     | pony     |
| Flower   | azalea  | daffodil | begonia   | daisy  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

