.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, taxi, van, trike
There 4 different types of food: lime, strawberry, blueberry, grapefruit
1. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating lime##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person driving the trike is the person eating lime##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the bike##1
7. the person driving the van is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Transport   | van  | trike      | bike        | taxi     |
| Food         | blueberry | lime | grapefruit | strawberry   |

