.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, iced-tea, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, ivory, yellow, lilac
1. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes turquise is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who likes turquise is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee   | lemonade   | iced-tea | milk |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Color     | ivory | turquise        | lilac       | yellow  |

