.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, weightlifting, golf
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, american, mexican, nigerian
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
2. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the japanese is the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the american##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Sport    | weightlifting   | golf      | handball       | cycling |
| Hobby   | camping | woodworking | sudoku     | fishing |
| Nationality     | nigerian     | american  | japanese | mexican |

