.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, australian, german, polish
City: nizza, venice, paris, san-francisco
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, horse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is the australian##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the australian##3
5. the russian is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the polish##1
7. the person traveling to nizza is the russian##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality      | german   | polish          | australian | russian        |
| City   | paris     | venice | san-francisco   | nizza     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goat         | horse         | guinea-pig |

