.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, horror, drama, comedy
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, train, car
1. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
2. the person watching drama movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the scooter is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Movie-Genre           | horror  | drama  | comedy | mystery |
| Transport   | car      | train | scooter         | skateboard    |

