.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, october, january, may
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, hiking, woodworking, gardening
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the manager is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Birthday   | october         | march  | january     | may         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| Hobby      | hiking         | woodworking  | skydiving   | gardening |

