.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dannemann, baccarat, bluemaster
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, orchid, bellflower
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 2. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is between the dannemann-smoker and the game-smoker##2
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
 8. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growsdaisy is between the bluemaster-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##2
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar   | game  | baccarat    | dannemann | bluemaster    |
| Flower   | poppy | orchid | daisy  | bellflower |
| Pet           | lizard   | mouse    | dog        | horse   |

