.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, cycling, ice-hockey, volleyball
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, house, soul, d&b
1. the fan of house is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the argentine##2
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the australian##1
5. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
9. the turkish is between the fan of soul and the fan of electronic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Sport      | snowboarding | ice-hockey      | cycling  | volleyball    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Music-Genre           | d&b      | soul       | house   | electronic      |

