The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, manager, pilot, doctor
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, musical, comedy, mystery
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person watching superhero movies##2
3. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the doctor is between the person watching superhero movies and the coach##2
7. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
8. the manager is in an even position##4
9. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
