4. the person drinking cola is the ranch-style house##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the craftsman house is the nurse##1
7. the security-guard is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the project-manager is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| House   | ranch-style | craftsman      | futuristic | townhouse |
| Job           | musician   | nurse  | security-guard     | project-manager |

