1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person who likes red and the owner of the hamster##2
6. the person who likes white is the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Pet       | hamster   | rat | frog | chinchilla |
| Color   | yellow | aquamarine      | red    | white   |

