1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the person eating tomato##2
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | tomato  | cabbage   | lemon    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | cooking     | chess | traveling |
| Cigar   | davidoff   | chaman | vegafina | aristoff   |

