.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy, daffodil, zinnia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel, zombie, disaster
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsaconite##2
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Flower   | zinnia | daisy | aconite | daffodil      |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel   | adventure        | disaster   | zombie       |

 